    attributes: Npc_TabantaHatago001
    contents:
      - control:
          kind: sound
          unknown:
            - 0
            - 4
      - text: "到了這把年紀，\n想起的盡是孩提時代的回憶啊。\n話雖如此，這種邊境"
      - control:
          kind: pause
          length: short
